    {
      "id": "1954750c-f3ba-80d1-bfef-ff2edcb0079f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The knowledge state is obtained via a gated graph NN and uses CNN to obtain embedding representations of exercises and skills. Moreover, there is a second mechanism to obtain embeddings of knowledge states. Finally, an Attention mechanism is used to make predictions.",
